{"tid":6073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解港女咁鐘意閪面？","createTime":"2016-11-27T07:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T15:16:37.000Z","uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b586244397c249bef92c9c73c361b4556e54764","tid":6073,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:25:34.000Z","msg":"頭先去茶記食個午餐，<br />\n附近大約有三枱情侶，四枱一家大細，<br />\n啲女人由十幾歲到四十歲都有，<br />\n但係個個都閪口閪面，<br />\n有一枱老母仲係咁鬧個仔，<br />\n情侶就閪住面各自玩手機！<br />\n<br />\n唯獨有一枱自由行，三個廿幾歲靚女有講有笑，打扮好貴氣，食嘢又唔會掛住玩手機。<br />\n<br />\n查實我地用畢生嘅心力去溝個女神，<br />\n最後都係同枱食飯各自玩手機，<br />\n仲日日閪面，為的是屌個閪，值咩？"},{"pid":"824ac014f998aefb615f4d23e4484417b2b5d92d","tid":6073,"uid":15346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:29:17.000Z","msg":"女神根本同隻兵冇野好講 唔㩒手機有咩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017f4723e2426a2bbb46abdff74c63cb97333ae6","tid":6073,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女神根本同隻兵冇野好講 唔㩒手機有咩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得有十年大將軍咁on9嘅物體出現！<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\n兵只係負責護送、拎嘢同付款，冇得屌架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d6724c9401bdaecc229343c0cd38dba1453eda","tid":6073,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:54:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老味啦自由行<br />\n上去溝支那女人啦，好行唔送 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b114f8867ff36e0520e13d464aa7a5b2917a91","tid":6073,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:55:41.000Z","msg":"港女閪面圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMhF22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMhF22.jpg&h=92d1c4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdXX8u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdXX8u.jpg&h=0